.DT
set_save_dir
Disk World creator help
set_save_dir

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_save_dir -  This method sets the save file associated with the controller.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_save_dir(string fname)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^fname%^RESET%^ - the save file
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/craft_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the save file associated with the controller.  The save
file should actually be a directory, the name of the directory plus a
.o will be used for the save files.  The directory must exist or weird
errors will occur.
This should always be set in the setup function of the room.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_controller(), query_save_dir()

.EP

